Insider Activity


Individual




John Bendoraitis



Mr. John Bendoraitis is Chief Operating Officer & Senior Vice President at Spirit Airlines, Inc.
Mr. Bendoraitis was previously employed as Chief Operating Officer by Frontier Airlines, Inc., President by Comair, Inc., President by Compass Airlines, Inc., and Vice President-Base Maintenance Operations by Northwest Airlines Corp.
He received his undergraduate degree from Metropolitan State University and an MBA from St. Thomas University (Florida).



