As Senior Vice President and Chief Operating Officer at SPIRIT AIRLINES INC, John  Bendoraitis  made $1,297,819 in total compensation.  Of this total $352,750 was received as a salary, $381,398 was received as a bonus, $0 was received in stock options, $555,496 was awarded as stock and $8,175 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


